      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification result — hemolysis index spread",
      "description": "Monte Carlo UQ over rheological model parameters and boundary condition variability. 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains below clinical threshold at 3 of 5 operating points; 2 points show marginal exceedance within uncertainty bounds."
    }
  ],
  "hasCredibilityFactor": [
    {
