      "rationale": "The CFD solver has a partial QMS implementation. Regression tests cover only 60% of relevant flow regimes. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent must demonstrate solver correctness for rotating-frame Navier-Stokes with non-Newtonian viscosity models.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for Newtonian flow only. Non-Newtonian hemolysis transport equation not independently verified. Gap to required level 4 remains significant."
    },
    {
