      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI analysis on at least three systematically refined meshes; GCI < 2% on hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed; GCI on pressure-head QoI is 1.8% but GCI on hemolysis index reaches 6.4% due to sensitivity in high-shear blade-tip regions. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
