      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rms) on hemolysis index QoI must be computed with uncertainty bounds; agreement within ±15% across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions deviate from experimental values by 18–42% across operating points. Uncertainty bounds computed via Monte Carlo but do not encompass experimental values at 2 operating points. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
