      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must use the same pump geometry, operating envelope, and blood analog as the COU. Extrapolation distance must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "Validation used FDA generic pump geometry which differs from the COU device in impeller tip clearance. Operating envelope partially overlaps. Extrapolation distance not formally quantified. Achieved level 3."
