      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters (viscosity coefficients, hemolysis model exponents, inlet velocity profiles) must have documented uncertainty distributions derived from experimental characterization.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis model exponents taken from literature without experimental re-characterization for the specific blood analog used. Inlet velocity profiles assumed fully developed without measurement. Epistemic gap."
    },
