      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size must be sufficient to characterize inter-sample variability in hemolysis index; minimum n=5 replicates per operating point with statistical analysis.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump dataset provides n=2 replicates at most operating points. Inter-sample variability cannot be reliably characterized. Epistemic gap flagged; factor not assessed."
