    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile review, the package is accepted for submission. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ was performed and documents uncertainty bounds on the hemolysis index QoI. The assessment team acknowledges that the package does not satisfy Complete profile requirements — in particular, a formal Requirement object (REQ-COU2-001) is described within the validation result narrative but has not been linked via a top-level bindsRequirement property. This structural gap is consistent with the Minimal profile scope and is recorded here for traceability.",
